75
00:03:14,860 --> 00:03:18,040
Keep in mind, the USMCA has been agreed on,

76
00:03:18,040 --> 00:03:19,560
but not ratified.

77
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:20,650
It still needs to be approved

78
00:03:20,650 --> 00:03:23,300
by each of the three countries’ legislatures,

79
00:03:23,300 --> 00:03:25,670
which probably won’t happen till early next
year.

80
00:03:25,670 --> 00:03:27,849
But regardless, Canada’s Prime Minister
Trudeau

81
00:03:27,849 --> 00:03:31,170
still says that despite the USMCA’s restrictions,

82
00:03:31,170 --> 00:03:34,950
