152
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:29,979
would be willing to have more openness

153
00:06:29,979 --> 00:06:32,840
for foreign reporters to go into Tibet,

154
00:06:32,840 --> 00:06:35,430
where they’ve been banned from traveling
for years.

155
00:06:35,430 --> 00:06:37,150
And Cui says, well,

156
00:06:37,150 --> 00:06:39,460
the altitude in Tibet is kind of high,

157
00:06:39,460 --> 00:06:41,540
